<p>Minimum 5 days before race start check-in will be active. Deadline for check-in is <b>24h</b>
before the race start. Every SL-Driver is required to react in #check-in channel. Reserves can also
react if they are able to race.<br><br>
20h before race start the race direction will announce which drivers will drive tomorrow's
race. In case SL-Drivers are reacted with X Reserve drivers will take their places. This information
